        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/rainfall/check",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["rainfall", "check"]
        },
        "description": "Lluvia acumulada en la cuenca del Salado (25 de Mayo, BsAs) durante el período de la inundación de verano 2016-2017. Debería devolver acumulados muy por encima de la media climática."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "TWI — SRTM (Salado 2017)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"polygon\": {\n    \"coordinates\": [\n      [\n        [-60.20, -35.48],\n        [-60.13, -35.48],\n        [-60.13, -35.42],\n        [-60.20, -35.42],\n        [-60.20, -35.48]\n      ]\n    ]\n  }\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/analysis/twi",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["analysis", "twi"]
        },
        "description": "TWI sobre el mismo polígono. La pampa deprimida tiene pendientes muy bajas → TWI alto (zonas que acumulan agua)."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Flood detection — Sentinel-1 (Pakistán Sindh 2022) [GARANTIZADO]",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"polygon\": {\n    \"coordinates\": [\n      [\n        [67.80, 27.50],\n        [67.90, 27.50],\n        [67.90, 27.60],\n        [67.80, 27.60],\n        [67.80, 27.50]\n      ]\n    ]\n  },\n  \"pre_event\": {\n    \"start_date\": \"2022-06-01\",\n    \"end_date\": \"2022-07-15\"\n  },\n  \"post_event\": {\n    \"start_date\": \"2022-08-25\",\n    \"end_date\": \"2022-09-30\"\n  }\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/analysis/flood",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["analysis", "flood"]
        },
        "description": "Inundaciones monzónicas Pakistán 2022 (Sindh, distrito Larkana). El evento cubrió ~33% del país. Ventanas amplias, S1A+S1B activos, cobertura excelente. pick_best_track elige automáticamente el track con mejor cobertura simétrica. flood_detected esperado = true con delta_vv_db muy negativo."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Flood detection — Sentinel-1 (Idai 2019 Pungwe — coords v2)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"polygon\": {\n    \"coordinates\": [\n      [\n        [34.65, -19.85],\n        [34.75, -19.85],\n        [34.75, -19.75],\n        [34.65, -19.75],\n        [34.65, -19.85]\n      ]\n    ]\n  },\n  \"pre_event\": {\n    \"start_date\": \"2019-02-15\",\n    \"end_date\": \"2019-03-10\"\n  },\n  \"post_event\": {\n    \"start_date\": \"2019-03-18\",\n    \"end_date\": \"2019-04-05\"\n  }\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/analysis/flood",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["analysis", "flood"]
        },
        "description": "Idai 2019 con coords movidas al este — planicie del río Pungwe, zona realmente catastróficamente inundada (la del oeste de Buzi quedaba en terreno más elevado). pick_best_track elige automáticamente. Esperamos flood_detected=true."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Flood detection — Sentinel-1 (RS Brasil 2024) [PRIMARY DEMO]",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"polygon\": {\n    \"coordinates\": [\n      [\n        [-51.65, -30.10],\n        [-51.58, -30.10],\n        [-51.58, -30.04],\n        [-51.65, -30.04],\n        [-51.65, -30.10]\n      ]\n    ]\n  },\n  \"pre_event\": {\n    \"start_date\": \"2024-04-10\",\n    \"end_date\": \"2024-04-25\"\n  },\n  \"post_event\": {\n    \"start_date\": \"2024-05-08\",\n    \"end_date\": \"2024-05-25\"\n  },\n  \"orbit\": \"DESCENDING\",\n  \"flood_threshold_db\": -17.0,\n  \"min_flooded_area_pct\": 5.0\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/analysis/flood",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["analysis", "flood"]
        },
        "description": "Demo principal: Inundación catastrófica de Rio Grande do Sul (Brasil), mayo 2024. Polígono ~7×7 km en Eldorado do Sul (planicie del río Jacuí). Pre seco (abril) vs post bajo agua (mayo). Caso limpio sin cuerpos de agua permanentes — se espera flood_detected=true, delta_vv_db muy negativo, flood_days > 14."
      },
      "response": []
    },
